      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single scratch or swirl mark, and the interior still has that new-car smell with absolutely no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is flawless; the engine performs with precision and the handling is as sharp as the day it rolled off the lot. For a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, this is the perfect example. It comes with a full service history and all original documentation.",
