    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable point-A-to-point-B driver. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows significant signs of age, including noticeable exterior scratches, some interior upholstery wear, and a suspension that will likely need attention in the coming year. It has been regularly serviced, but a new owner should expect to invest in some minor cosmetic and mechanical refreshments to bring it back to its best. It's a solid, honest car for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few pending projects.",
