    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering an uncompromising 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring optimal lateral grip and suspension kinematics. Performance-critical maintenance has been prioritized, including proactive rod bearing replacement and reinforced throttle actuators. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, complemented by a robust subframe and refreshed bushings. While the aesthetics reflect its honest history as a weekend tourer, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain response are superlative for the discerning enthusiast.",
