      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, having been predominantly garage-kept, with only minor road-wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a rigorous service schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. Included are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service records. This is an excellent opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
